| 3 | A: V-S5, B: V-S6 | Effects-Map + Rule-Strategy | 2 parallel |
| 4a | A: BlockInserter, B: BlockToolbar, C: ReaderView | Component-Tests | 3 parallel |
| 4b | — | Manuelle QA: Block-Ops, Styles, Backward-Compat | manuell |
| Arch | A: Deps+Types, B: No-Index-Invariante | Architektur-Compliance | 2 parallel |

